	* MonoDevelop.Ide.Gui.Pads/DefaultMonitorPad.cs: Make sure the pad
	  can't be reused once the monitor operation has started.
	* MonoDevelop.Ide.Debugging/DebugExecutionHandlerFactory.cs,
